{"tid":2002760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得香港人嘅廣東話好小眾","createTime":"2020-05-05T11:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T12:17:36.000Z","uid":239942,"like":5,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"13f7b58ece7803a7d0d0172532de57d7e980a383","tid":2002760,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"我地以外就只有海外華僑同廣東人識講<br />\n反而英文法文德文日文韓文同中文都有好多人識講<br />\n好似去到邊都好lonely <br />\n大部分香港人英文又未好到mother tongue 咁，去到其他地方只可以同香港人圍爐<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅軟實力亦不及全盛時期咁<br />\n曾經係asia嘅中心，<br />\n而家唔計金融真係拎出手黎威嘅人同事都冇<br />\n<br />\n唯一可以做就係笑9中國人，屌"},{"pid":"ccc78f6264a1b4320dbfb78d5c180cb1aabd4010","tid":2002760,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溫馨提示提提大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">西樹泡芙係紅色資本</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早幾日見到超級多後生女排買二送二個優惠<br />\n可能有啲人未知<br />\n但希望如果知道嘅人以後搵其他嘢取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買西樹泡芙之前可否停一停諗一諗?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739594</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"10ca006eed560d4c20f9bb17af0f7c0fd61f5705","tid":2002760,"uid":159796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"係, 所以上年香港個個都識就係因為屌大陸"},{"pid":"6d8ad2e5b0ba88ab4682b7013fc76403751af7e4","tid":2002760,"uid":34970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"小眾都未係大問題，有好多港豬家長都係重英文/蝗語而輕粵語"},{"pid":"b5c18939120074ff3a650cdb09aca8a02e461a5b","tid":2002760,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:27:15.000Z","msg":"贊成，所以會學埋英文"},{"pid":"a09adc6dcd3f54f223d83c3c42cf7e4a75e71b90","tid":2002760,"uid":273545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"廣東使用粵語的人口大約有6700萬，加上廣